➜宽哥：《西江月·倦》（外一首）
http://www.sohu.com/a/427141954_100115135	14265
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201025/37fdca6dd6ee446282a3bd6ad7dd1da3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《西江月.倦》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>———词林正韵</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong> 文/宽哥</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">萧瑟秋风花谢，身累思绪迷茫。又兼任重事繁忙，沈沈温床锦帐。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人倦新书厌读，闲愁玉液浇肠。凭高长夜独凄凉，强把新词高唱。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201025/831fd0e046d349a89424e19be6ea16f3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《西江月·重阳》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>———词林正韵</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong> 文/宽哥</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">昨日潇湘别浦，今朝南粤鹏城。莺歌笑语曲阑行，晚照风摇斜影。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">重九登高又望，音容梦里常萦。菊香杯满意长情，莫负期颐欢庆。</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
