➜广东诗人小隐：西江月．重阳
http://www.sohu.com/a/427146302_100115135	15558
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201025/08ca054137f7477191bf29f8bab18673.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>西江月．重阳</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/小隐</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">薄雾潇潇秋雨，淡烟袅袅芭蕉。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">多情应笑我今朝，故土相思难了。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">梦里菊花香远，东篱陶韵飘飘。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">家乡归处路迢迢，九九重阳酒少。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201025/ea0f852188114db48a2754469bbe2669.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
