➜浙江诗人虞崇庄：游径山寺（外一首）
http://www.sohu.com/a/427147107_100115135	15909
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201025/ebf6a2dae5c84944a70380c51b22a133.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> <strong>游径山寺</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/虞崇庄</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">金秋游古刹，红日照云岑。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鸟语林间啭，流泉石上吟。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">荒阶苔藓暗空院落花深。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">四顾俱闲寂，惟闻梵磬音。</p>
