➜河南诗人樊国文：七律•重阳
http://www.sohu.com/a/427148567_100115135	16768
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201025/ec5a27bddd244f3e8e7534a3a2239285.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七律•重阳</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/樊国文</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>其一（平水韵六麻）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">遥想当年故里家，破屋残壁绕篱笆。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">同攀胡寨寻仙草，独涉湍河捕野鸭。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">快乐柴房喝桂酒，开心湖畔赏菊花。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">登高回望乡关路，缕缕忧愁蔽晚霞。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201025/8badb50b80894114b7e43ef4fed33910.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>其二（平水韵七阳）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鼠年再度遇重阳，锦绣河山万里霜。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">丹桂有情方酿酒，金菊无虑又飘香。</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
