<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201025/4056c44fd3a741cd92af0a37b6be53e8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
➜广西诗人陈熠明：重阳梦里念亲恩
http://www.sohu.com/a/427150807_100115135	17490
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>重阳梦里念亲恩</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>现代诗原创作品·心灵诗幻陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201025/6c7149a7e9fb474683e321258ea444fe.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(一)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">站在山上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">站在这高高的山上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>可我看不到啊</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>再也看不到父亲</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一行远去了尘世的足迹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">重阳的风</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">用青霜凝固了我的泪滴</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>拾起山野里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那每一叶飘落了过往的记忆</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我在</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">秋风里追寻</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>追寻着父亲你</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一句装满了善念的谚语</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是我的灵魂</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在跟随着山风落下</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>落下那一个</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>深邃了想念的谷底</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">父亲你在哪里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你是飘荡在行云的高处</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>还是隐入了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>流星那一夜梦幻的迷离</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(二)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">站在云边</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">站在这茫茫的云边</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>可我听不到啊</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>再也听不到母亲</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一心远去了尘世的笑</strong>语</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">重阳的山</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">用晨雾笼罩了我的影子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>拾起山野里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那每一叶纷飞了相逢的记忆</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我在</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">秋风里追寻</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>追寻着母亲你</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一句装满了五谷的谚语</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是我的影子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在跟随着太阳荡去</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>荡去那一个</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>遥远了怀念的天际</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">母亲你在哪里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你是流淌在天河的深处</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>还是隐入了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>山野那一歌天籁的小溪</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201025/30a15735db5f48d6b996f87e13fa0aa9.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(三)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我不想错过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不想错过那每一个梦里的消息</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一颗心总是</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>想着在梦里跨越</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">跨越过阴阳</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">界上去和你们相聚</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>每一个醒来</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>的梦都是一个失落</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">失落了我的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">记忆也失落了我的想起</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>我每一次都想</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>都想从梦里带着你们归去</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可奈何桥上的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">阴阳线还是割断了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">割断了黎明和割断了黄昏的走起</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>贿赂着</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>上千亿的冥币</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但还是打通不了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">天地那一道森严规矩</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(四)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>我不想错过</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>不想错过那每一个梦里的奇遇</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一颗心总是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">想着在梦里跨越</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>跨越过乾坤</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>界上去和你们团聚</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">每一个醒来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">的梦都是一个落寞</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>落寞了我的</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>未来也落寞了我的过去</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我每一次都想</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都想从梦里缠着你们归去</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>可奈何桥上的</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>孟婆汤还是淹没了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>淹没了离去和淹没了归来的孤旅</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">贿赂着</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">上千万的冥衣</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>但还是打通不了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>天地那一道森严的戒律</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201025/3cd2b839b2ad43bcaac2d1eb4f9a66ae.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(五)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">仰望着高山</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">孩儿就会想起</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>想起父亲您那一双</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>高高地耸入了云霄的肩膀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">孩儿看见您</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>看见您用肩膀在</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>黎明里和黄昏里扛起</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">扛起</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">生命里那每一个</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>沉重了天南</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>和沉重了地北的日子</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">忘不了许多个</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">太阳出来的早晨</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>您在田地里努力地</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>风动着那一把沉睡了千年的铁犁</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">您说那</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">铁犁是一支笔</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一支可以绘画出</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>了丰收和希望的铁笔</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">孩儿看见</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">您的汗滴洒落在</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>洒落在您脚下</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一片苍茫了希望的大地</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(六)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">俯视着流水</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">孩儿就会想起</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>想起母亲您那一双</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>深深地没入了水底的眼光</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">孩儿看见您</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>看见您用眼光</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>在早出和晚归里锁定</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">锁定起</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">生命里那每一脉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>滋养了春夏</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>和滋养了秋冬的流溪</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">忘不了许多个</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">月亮升起的夜晚</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>您在</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>青灯下着迷地</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">风动着那一轮</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">沉睡了千年的纺车</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>您说那</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>纺车是一个迷</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一个可以隐藏起</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">了青春和年华的歌迷</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>孩儿看见</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>您的白发闪烁在</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">闪烁在您耳边</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一片沧桑了流年的眼里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201025/59a8c673812a4102a4ebc9b3b746f8a9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(七)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>等来了霜降</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>等来了晚秋里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>又一个天高云淡的日子</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">孩儿把</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">隔断阴阳的脚步</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>拉长在黄昏</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一个日落的西去</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">飘荡在</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">风中的记忆</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>再也</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>留不住孩儿</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">为你们写下那几</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">行风动了泪眼的诗句</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(八)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>打落了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>青霜的鸟语</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">把自己的歌声</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">交给了怀念的距离</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>孩儿要在</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>月亮升起之前找到</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">找到你们那一心</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">曾经灿烂过了花开的笑语</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>在长夜</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>里等一场梦</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">等来重阳夜</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一场通往天国的梦</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>孩儿才能</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>给你们寄上啊</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">寄上那几套</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">遥遥地跨越了思念的冥币</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201025/7d86b8af6559497a93412be0d07c85c5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(九)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>等来了霜降</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>等来了重阳里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>又一个红叶灿烂的节气</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">孩儿把</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">望断阴阳的眼泪</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>抛落在天涯</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那一个茫茫的天宇</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">颤抖在</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">风中的纸笔</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>再也</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>写不出孩儿</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">对你们说出</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一番浮动了轮回的言语</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(十)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>嘶哑了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>呼唤的长笛</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">把自己的心声</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">沉入了黑暗的地狱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>孩儿要在</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>长夜来临之前找到</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">找到你们那一片</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">曾经踏破过了坎坷的足迹</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>在黄昏</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>里等一场梦</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">等来重阳夜</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一场通往天国的梦</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>孩儿才能</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>给你们寄上啊</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">寄上那几套</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">遥遥地温暖了思念的寒衣</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201025/35abdd87dd064b0d9a63b422a4017d81.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>▲<strong>【作者简介】：</strong>陈熠明，笔名心灵诗幻，男，1976年生，广西平果市人。爱好文学创作，曾有诗歌作品发布于多家报刊杂志和网络。时任星连文学社副社长。职业于中医，热衷于传统文化传播。诗是文笔与文笔的向往，诗是朋友与朋友的交心。诗是千难和万险的将来，诗是岁月与年华的渴望。诗是春夏和秋冬的风景，诗是父亲和母亲的嘱咐，诗是父亲和母亲的叮咛。诗是渡船与碧波的远航，诗是生命与大海的彼岸。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201025/ceec15e2230d4979a3da8f4fe1977ece.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>❖星连文学社管理团队：</strong></p>
<p>★ <strong>名誉社长:</strong>叶仲录 ☆<strong>总顾问:</strong>薛依云 ☆<strong>首席顾问:</strong>欧大象 ☆<strong>执行顾问:</strong>岩心（薛莹） ☆<strong>顾问团成员:</strong>欧大象（文光）、岩心（薛莹）、石秉旺、陈文化、高原红、碧海（陈碧珍)、黄香玉 ☆<strong>社长兼总编:</strong>星连 ☆<strong>常务副社长:</strong>岩心（薛莹） ☆<strong>副社长:</strong>丁冬亮、绝尘道长、梁继权、高晓园、陈熠明、东晓 、木子 ☆<strong>艺术总监:</strong>陆廷教 ☆<strong>编委会主任:</strong>听尘居士 ☆<strong>编委会成员:</strong>孤客、黄香玉、星连、枫叶、绮雯、徐玉兰、叶仲录、薛依云、高晓园、田书芹、木子……（添加中） ☆<strong>主编:</strong>游散居士 ☆<strong>副主编：</strong> 丁冬亮、闫加辉、张立标、张君霞</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201025/bd32b04f596b49db83ab68845edd826b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201025/41e3b5c977614316948dc0f7c31899e6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>❖主编简介：</strong></p>
<p>▲笔名：星连、星连193，原名：卢链生，号游散居士，别号：中原听真，男，汉族，七零后，籍贯：广东汕尾，现居深圳。系中国诗联协会理事，中国诗词协会会员，世界汉诗协会会员，中国网络诗歌学会会员，河北采风学会会员，中原诗词研究会会员，太行诗词协会会员，认证诗人，网站签约作家。2014年受江西电台连线采访，作品散发各大网站及入选各类诗集、文集等，诗歌及其他作品曾获特等奖、一等奖、二等奖、铜奖、优秀奖各类奖项。主要结集作品有：诗集《爱情与人生》，长篇小说《漂泊》、《江湖客传》、《都市迷情之情仇恩怨》，小说集《百味人生》以及散文集等。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201025/37ae115190204f4d8915dcac750b5acc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>❖郑重声明:</strong></p>
