<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201025/300bc47bdfb14743881f8793b6491d58.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
➜星连（广东）：《星连古诗词汇总》
http://www.sohu.com/a/427246729_100115135	60167
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201026/1c396ca3b0994598a7423f0011986bc4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝·相思漏（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">繁花尽故愁，素色愿独流。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">情入君行处，相思雨满楼。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.7.18</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝·酷暑（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">天炉火较真，汗落觅无痕。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">念想一场雪，梅香赋古心。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019-7-18</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝·等爱（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">碧宇心间静，闲茶等爱归。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">夜风稍作信，声到已开眉。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.7.18</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝·留香（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">常行知路远，静坐感天长。</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
