<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">身处江湖乱，心留一炷香。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.7.19</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝·心韵（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">寻芳季已迟，落魄却成诗。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">几缕清香过，牵情韵满池。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.7.19</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201026/8d3c2f3a0d214bd895a804a8a9d44550.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝·世风（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">日晚鸟归林，千峰静入心。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">闻书知圣理，对比叹红尘。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.7.19</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝·雪念（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">长思意可连，片语入情天。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">抚曲千花逊，炉香缕缕闲。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.7.20</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.孤夜（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">临窗夜语听，帘动入诗风。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一卷浮沉事，参差两处空。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.7.21</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.无题（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">曲和百年情，相交玉露生。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">沉吟常带泪，烟雨又朦胧。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.7.21</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.独（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">红尘怨几多，心泪早成河。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">日暮人皆去，千言自诉说。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.7.21</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201026/3d31da7bc1564a04b623179e5f20b05d.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.落花（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">枝上无长日，君情怎可伤？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">相约尘世路，<strong>心步窃词香。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.7.22</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.流水（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">意入映清光，花衣且掖藏。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">寻君无定世，梦复到天荒。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.7.22</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.闲情（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">冷暖各心知，风摇半阕痴。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">归闲俗世远，对晚意成诗。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.7.22</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.唯君（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">尘世几相逢，唯君慰此生。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">抛开花月事，誓守只真情。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.7.23</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.观潮（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">情海拢千流，涛声日月悠。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人生多少事，一笑在回眸。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.7.25</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201026/5d3478ea55ea4846b883afc716b8b6ba.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.花意（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">沧海誓无空，心栖万古情，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">三生约未尽，轮待见春红。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.7.26</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.醉月（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">诗勾故岸声，对饮月常明。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">长望天涯处，三分醉不同。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.7.27</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.乘兴（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">心开兴满楼，带醉上花丘。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">指抚云溪梦，诗勺舀画流。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.7.27</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.小白（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">万物自缘因，相邻客不新。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">吠声临夜响，日暖卧泉心。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.7.28</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.炎暑（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">风丝尽烈阳，暑气扫还扬。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">书卷清流引，心池静客香。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.7.28</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201026/7e09565419f147868158788c8725ef2c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.横流（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">万欲不离心，横流世上人。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">诗词魂已远，静里看乾坤。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.7.29</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.诗夏（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">落夜心归静，风凉暑气消。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">寄思千里外，字句懒推敲。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.7.29</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.心景（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">苍山近月容，庐舍意长生。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">入梦云成语，归来世事空。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.8.3</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.远尘（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">诗意古留痕，闲情景自临。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">云山别苦梦，烟暖鸟鸣春。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.8.3</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.问（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">多少尘间事，思来昨日同。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">箫声谁可解？夕照满江红。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.8.4</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201026/b0d24ca49b50401f8be33a4fd18f62d0.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.满江红（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">随流两岸空，心念见云峰。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">客问无人复，来年再作同。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.8.4</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.夏图（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">入耳蝉声翠，开轩境意先。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">晨风粘句影，悄落嫁诗前。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.8.4</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.别（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一别千里远，事过复情伤。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">花落听愁语，思中欲断肠。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.8.5</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝.无题（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">独梦长更入冷秋，忍将牵挂向闲流。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">诗含万语何人诉？情动红尘泪不休。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.8.5</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝.暮吟（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">半眠归舍半吟秋，日落门前影渐收。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只恐闲情无去处，心言满纸对高楼。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.8.5</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201026/a6adb89eb7744de1985cf5a8354f6928.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.有情（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">望风知冷暖，世故入人生。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">月下多悄语，闲流不忘情。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.8.6</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝. 立秋寄语（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">盛夏去无痕，红尘百念深。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">花前诗尽意，秋影却酬心。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.8.8</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.独语（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">落夜思花语，秋声半入闲。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">情心犹作意，琴曲问谁弹。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.8.10</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.问禅（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">薄云风写意，楼角夜归空。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">若问禅何处，高瞻事可同<strong>。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.8.12</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.醉剑（新旧韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一醉云山浅，随心剑影流。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人间春不灭，禅路苦中求。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.8.12</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201026/b7244e2c053047e39091ec1d8d3fab3b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.衣渐老（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">心由圆梦始，写意几分情。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">欲醉千花慢，沾衣细雨轻。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.8.14</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.借景（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">沿河景色新，柳静候伊人。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">笑意通南北，诗还万里春。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.8.16</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.断剑（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">残影半留踪，江湖四面风。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">马啼声未止，断剑对谁空？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.8.17</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.尘客（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文／星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">花落只因情，尘埃伴客行。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">千愁吟不尽，变幻是人生。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.8.17</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.入念（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文／星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">尘路万般伤，回眸泪迹长。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">无间还岁月，今世共沧桑。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.8.18</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201026/caf8cb5b53e94007911e527b8af276e7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.三叶草（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文／星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">谁解人间爱，天涯问月明。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">含情心不老，落地意长青。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.8.19</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.炊烟（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文／星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">秋来句自填，入梦见炊烟。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">草木寻风处，柴门对影怜。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.8.19</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.独秋（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文／星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">秋入景依然，长情不尽天。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">枝头千缕意，梦里落君前。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.8.29</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>渔歌子.相思阕（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文／星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">忍看残红落梦帘，雁声何处觅缠绵。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">思不尽，意还连，千樽水月寄云天。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.9.4</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝.无题（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">百念千思病已成，人间难舍是深情。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">西风不解其中意，花落坟前点点红。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019-9.5</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.守夜（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文／星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">红尘泪几滴？夜半问相依。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">影入千思眼，难为梦又期。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.9.20</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.解秋（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文／星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">空茫色尽连，事入寄云间。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">风静尘埃落，秋心忍作闲。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.9.20</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201026/91db6d7bc0ef4722ab99c1a861eef1ee.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.秋夜（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文／星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">句自念思得，深更意又合。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">情愁终不尽，忍却语无多。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.9.22</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.思君（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">琴心未敢抛，秋晚对闲潮。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">常以君为曲，吟思在夙宵。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.10.4</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.心音（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">已是秋将晚，何时见会期？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">思深难作断，敢与海天齐。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.10.5</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.重阳感怀（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">心听九月秋，云露问谁休。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">别后红尘老，诗声忍自流。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.10.7</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.独秋（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">繁华几处怜？伤忆任词闲。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人又深秋里，江中水自寒。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.10.9</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201026/d6cc15491dea478daa91770289b87374.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.醉问（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">叶落心归景，浮生几度伤。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">常觉知夜浅，引醉问情长。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.10.9</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.品（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">万事随秋静，相邀是己心。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">茶中知百味，道岸可容人。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.10.12</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.无题（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">逢秋念自忙，云色映溪长。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">语尽红尘路，风来入夜凉。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.10.13</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.无题（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">千年故事深，梦去见孤魂。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">白露衔诗草，心香待有人。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.10.16</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.会（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">无意也归流，云低半抱秋。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">相逢常有日，衣色染清眸。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.10.16</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201026/634508c2610b4622b4a77803cc359b3e.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.祝（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一、</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">妙曲乐天情，心间祝意行。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">相思秋染色，日月伴君明。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>二、</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">日丽笑颜生，花香绕宇庭。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">举杯春祝语，惬意舞才情。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.10.20</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.无题（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">向北行千里，风寒碧暖心。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">云烟生若梦，闲卧醒诗魂。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.10.24</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.吟菇（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">灵品天来早，金黄入眼轻。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">云华心可探，何处不高情。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.11.5</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.题禅（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">灵门望若空，香影几随风。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">归处难寻迹，禅觉涧有声。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.11.6</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.题景（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">九曲魂归远，溪风入韵香。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">行吟山水意，禅化道心长。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.11.15</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201026/225a9802f8e04fe5b3aaaf1a4f00932a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.拈句（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">闲舟谁可渡？河畔影如常。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟红尘事，无约亦入凉。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.11.19</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.无题（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">月下几行思，当秋意若迟。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">繁华吟有处，旧曲换新知。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.11.19</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.提心 （新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">浮云千重意，戈壁几沧桑。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">无欲诗行远，情深墨自香。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.11.20</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.心岸（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">云以空为处，心随海角明。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">无尘禅自在，意入唤长生。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.11.23</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝.梦梅（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">寒山有影数梅香，几缕痴情几段伤。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">曲入红尘无尽处，心怀故事梦悠长。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.11.26</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.知月（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">秋露几分倾，寒江影自成。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">霞衣孤忍处，以换月长明。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.12.3</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201026/9e989f4d17784c2299898ec8ff6ada8e.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.独（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">云影三更醉，红尘事又新。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">思中独望月，景入见初心。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.12.9</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.迁（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">天地往来人，繁华剩几存？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">长街灯火暗，问过泪流心。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.12.29</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.留梦（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">多少是和非，人前事自悲。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">轻留三尺梦，老去不相陪。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.12.29</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.无题（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">舟行水路开，云暖望成台。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有意花如幻，无说道也来。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.12.29</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.梦（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有梦人成对，三阳喜气生。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">红尘无四季，情意写分明。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2019.12.31</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201026/8cf1d494b3ca48e5b908d0cd20ab9e7b.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.如夜（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">野径春留景，闲楼雨冷人。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不知君去处，难舍有情心。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2020.3.15</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.隔离（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">无意知秋晚，浮生梦几回。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">乾坤三斗米，冷暖度人归。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2020.3.18</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.崖（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">云峰天处止，落地寸间余。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">逐梦生来有，留心赴远期。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2020.3.22</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝.独问（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/星连</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">寒雨伴孤心，江湖几故人？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">清风留客醉，相忆苦中吟。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2020.3.23</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201025/f3318c19e4ac4fba93b13b65b5f0df71.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>▲<strong>【作者简介】：</strong>笔名：星连、星连193，原名：卢链生，号游散居士，别号；中原听真，男，汉族，七零后，籍贯：广东汕尾，现居深圳。中文专业，作家、诗人，社会学研究者，心理学研究者，情感剖释家。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201025/4063dd0ffd384bb5b52eef4b76654c5a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>❖星连文学社管理团队：</strong></p>
<p>★ <strong>名誉社长:</strong>叶仲录 ☆<strong>总顾问:</strong>薛依云 ☆<strong>首席顾问:</strong>欧大象 ☆<strong>执行顾问:</strong>岩心（薛莹） ☆<strong>顾问团成员:</strong>欧大象（文光）、岩心（薛莹）、石秉旺、陈文化、高原红、碧海（陈碧珍)、黄香玉 ☆<strong>社长兼总编:</strong>星连 ☆<strong>常务副社长:</strong>岩心（薛莹） ☆<strong>副社长:</strong>丁冬亮、绝尘道长、梁继权、高晓园、陈熠明、东晓 、木子 ☆<strong>艺术总监:</strong>陆廷教 ☆<strong>编委会主任:</strong>听尘居士 ☆<strong>编委会成员:</strong>孤客、黄香玉、星连、枫叶、绮雯、徐玉兰、叶仲录、薛依云、高晓园、田书芹、木子……（添加中） ☆<strong>主编:</strong>游散居士 ☆<strong>副主编:</strong>丁冬亮、闫加辉、张立标、张君霞</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201025/9c8d2fbbcf9141a0bcde0a3b93870229.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201025/8f3795d789024678832bebafdc9bde09.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>❖主编简介:</strong></p>
<p>▲笔名：星连、星连193，原名：卢链生，号游散居士，别号：中原听真，男，汉族，七零后，籍贯：广东汕尾，现居深圳。系中国诗联协会理事，中国诗词协会会员，世界汉诗协会会员，中国网络诗歌学会会员，河北采风学会会员，中原诗词研究会会员，太行诗词协会会员，认证诗人，网站签约作家。2014年受江西电台连线采访，作品散发各大网站及入选各类诗集、文集等，诗歌及其他作品曾获特等奖、一等奖、二等奖、铜奖、优秀奖各类奖项。主要结集作品有：诗集《爱情与人生》，长篇小说《漂泊》、《江湖客传》、《都市迷情之情仇恩怨》，小说集《百味人生》以及散文集等。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201025/d592c72954b543d8a2d2fbacb352162c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
