➜广东诗人辉哥：重阳
http://www.sohu.com/a/427251946_100115135	61106
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201026/6fda53a8bc74404ba6b074234ab5ff3f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>重阳</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/辉哥</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">果然九九艳阳天，云淡空明见蔚蓝；</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">节至重阳知岁晚，风来冷意感时迁；</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">常言秋景多金色，偏爱春花似玉颜；</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">逆旅人生何自在？中年痴梦水云间。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201026/cc8f0fc36c10412a954376734225c972.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>▲<strong>【作者简介】：</strong>围炉诗情辉哥，来自广东梅县客家，自小在客家农村长大，对客家文化情有独钟。喜爱古诗词，涂鸦作品多用于自耍。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201026/b0d16a429f444ab1bcf99d84d4ac2ca5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
